      "content": "Generate a single, self-contained HTML file with embedded CSS and JavaScript that demonstrates the concept Hash Table with MAXIMUM interactivity and rich user control. Focus on:\n\n- Multiple interactive controls (buttons, sliders, input fields)\n- Complex state transitions and user-driven workflows\n- Deep exploration capabilities with many possible interaction paths\n- Rich functionality as the PRIMARY goal\n\nIMPORTANT: Keep visual design EXTREMELY MINIMAL and BASIC - use simple black text on white background, basic HTML elements with no styling, no colors, no animations. The interface should be functional but visually plain and unpolished. Prioritize interactive richness over visual appeal.\n\nOnly respond with the complete HTML file.\n"
